::EndBringer/Demise/Greven/Killfest::

EndBringer, Demise, and Greven end up outside Astrotrain after he 
transforms. They look around briefly, EndBringer looking back at the 
Stunticon at the question.

"Hmm. I'll contact him. He should be here shortly."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Killfest looks up as a message from EndBringer comes through the 
internal communication system.

"Give Scyther what he needs," he says to Chamaleon, "I am needed 
elsewhere."

He turns and walks back to Darkfate. "Hey, how do I get out of this 
place and to the surface?"
